All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.microedition.lcdui.CommandListener
public class LoggerForm
extends javax.microedition.lcdui.Form
implements javax.microedition.lcdui.CommandListener

The LoggerForm is a screen that has the ability to log text.

Application can get the screen handle by getInstance() method and set the CommandListener to receive the command event using setExternalCommandListener method.

Version:
1.0
